Proud moment for the Wrights, as @salesforce awarded them the Service Equality Award today with their team by their side. This inaugural award was given to them for their dedication to equality in the workplace for people living with disabilities. It was presented to them during the keynote at the annual @dreamforce conference in San Francisco.
